        "text_q7mxfa": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>During deep sleep, the muscles around the jaw and throat can naturally relax. For some people, this relaxation may narrow the airway and create vibration — which is often heard as snoring.<br/><br/></p>",
