        "text_ULkbxX": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Trainixy™ Smart Anti-Snoring Device uses gentle Double Pulse TENS/EMS stimulation under the chin to help support the jaw and throat area during sleep. The built-in sensor helps detect snoring and automatically activates soft pulse stimulation when needed.<br/></p><p><strong>Advanced Sleep-Support Technology Made Simple</strong></p><p><strong>Double Pulse TENS/EMS:</strong><br/>Uses gentle dual-pulse stimulation under the chin to help support the muscles around the jaw and throat area.</p><p></p><p><strong>Auto Snore Detection:</strong><br/>Smart sensing technology helps recognize snoring and responds automatically without needing manual adjustment.</p><p><strong>One-Button Night Routine</strong><br/>Simple to use before bed — apply the patch, turn on the device, and let it support your sleep routine through the night.<br/></p>",
