        "text_RVJtFB": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Designed with gentle Double Pulse TENS/EMS technology, the Trainixy™ Smart Anti-Snoring Device helps support a quieter, more comfortable sleep routine — without mouthpieces, nose clips, or bulky straps.</p><p>Used consistently as part of your nightly routine, it works quietly under the chin while you sleep, helping you and your partner enjoy a calmer night.</p><p><strong>Designed to support better sleep comfort:</strong></p><p><strong>Auto </strong>detects snoring and responds with gentle pulse stimulation when needed</p><p><strong>12g </strong>ultra-lightweight design made for comfortable overnight wear</p><p><strong>10 hrs </strong>of nighttime use from approximately 1 hour of magnetic charging</p>",
            "alignment": "left",
            "mobile_alignment": "mobile-center",
            "text_size": 14,
            "enable_custom_color": false,
            "custom_text_color": "#FF0000",
            "margin_top": 15,
